(click:?page)[
    (goto: "Dang_Jelita_Warning_Start")
]


:: Courtyard_Quiet_Wind {"position":"1200,1300","size":"100,100"}
A brief silence follows as the wind carries the scent of the sea across the courtyard.

(click:?page)[
    (goto: "Hang_Dayang_Control_Not_Trade")
]


:: Dang_Jelita_Cannons {"position":"1000,1300","size":"100,100"}
“They speak of cannons and of tribute demanded by force.”

(click:?page)[
    (goto: "Hang_Dayang_Past_Powers")
]


:: Dang_Jelita_Entrance {"position":"900,400","size":"100,100"}
A voice calls out. Dang Jelita approaches with a basket of pepper pods, her tone playful.
(click:?page)[
    (goto: "Dang_Jelita_Playful_Intro")
]


:: Dang_Jelita_Laughing_Arguments {"position":"1200,500","size":"100,100"}
“Eighty-four tongues, all arguing over pepper and porcelain. If the traders ever agreed on anything, the earth might split open.”
(click:?page)[
    (goto: "Market_Choice_Hub")
]


:: Dang_Jelita_Legacy_Line {"position":"700,700","size":"100,100"}
“Some say Melaka became a favored state because our Sultan knelt to no one but the truth.”
(click:?page)[
    (goto: "Hang_Dayang_Ming_Respect")
]


:: Dang_Jelita_Playful_Intro {"position":"900,500","size":"100,100"}
“Dayang, you walk too fast for a scholar.”
(click:?page)[
    (goto: "Dang_Jelita_To_Protagonist")
]


:: Dang_Jelita_To_Protagonist {"position":"1000,500","size":"100,100"}
“You are new. I can always tell by the way you stare at everything as if it were precious. In Melaka, everything is precious, even the arguments.”
(click:?page)[
    (goto: "P_Asks_Arguments")
]


:: Dang_Jelita_Warning_Start {"position":"800,1300","size":"100,100"}
Dang Jelita approaches in a hurried manner. “The traders are uneasy. Portuguese ships linger beyond the straits. They do not come only to trade.”

(click:?page)[
    (goto: "Hang_Dayang_Not_Bow")
]


:: Dang_Jelita_Worried_Ships {"position":"800,1600","size":"100,100"}
Jelita speaks with a worried tone. “There is tension everywhere. Some ships leave early while others arrive armed.”
(click:?page)[
    (goto: "Hang_Dayang_Worried_Storm")
]


:: Dang_Jelita_ZhengHe_Normal {"position":"800,700","size":"100,100"}
Dang Jelita speaks with a calm, steady tone. “That is the legacy of Admiral Zheng He. His voyages protected Melaka from Siam long ago.”
(click:?page)[
    (goto: "Dang_Jelita_Legacy_Line")
]


